graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator Component"
        Manager[Manager Pod<br/>Deployment]
        RayController[RayCluster Controller]
        AppWrapperController[AppWrapper Controller]
        MutatingWebhook[Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        ValidatingWebhook[Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        MetricsService[Metrics Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        WebhookService[Webhook Service<br/>443→9443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertController[Cert Controller]

        Manager --> RayController
        Manager --> AppWrapperController
        Manager --> MutatingWebhook
        Manager --> ValidatingWebhook
        MetricsService --> Manager
        WebhookService --> MutatingWebhook
        WebhookService --> ValidatingWebhook
        CertController -->|manages certs| WebhookService
    end

    %% Custom Resources
    User[User/Notebook] -->|creates| RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
    User -->|creates| AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2]

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| RayController
    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| AppWrapperController

    %% Webhooks
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] -->|validates/mutates| MutatingWebhook
    K8sAPI -->|validates/mutates| ValidatingWebhook

    %% Created Resources - RayCluster
    RayController -->|creates| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>OpenShift]
    RayController -->|creates| Route[Route/Ingress<br/>ray-dashboard-*]
    RayController -->|creates| ClientRoute[Route<br/>ray-client-*<br/>10001/TCP mTLS]
    RayController -->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies<br/>Pod Isolation]
    RayController -->|creates| CASecret["CA Secret<br/>cluster-ca"]
    RayController -->|creates| TLSSecret["TLS Secret<br/>cluster-tls"]

    %% Created Resources - AppWrapper
    AppWrapperController -->|creates| WrappedResources[Wrapped Resources<br/>Jobs, Deployments, etc.]

    %% External Dependencies
    RayController -->|depends on| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.2.1]
    AppWrapperController -->|integrates| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.10.1+<br/>Batch Scheduling]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    RayController -.->|reads config| ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DSCInitialization]
    User -.->|UI| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    ODHDashboard -.->|creates| RayClusterCR

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| MetricsService

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style AppWrapperController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style MutatingWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style ValidatingWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RayClusterCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style AppWrapperCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style KubeRay fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Kueue fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
